  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Initial SEND screen is not aligned on iPhone 5S real device and does not match mocks \r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n**### Please note that it is not full list of discrapencies . The UI should match the mocks 1x1 , check https://zpl.io/a3eexl2**\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/30632657-94bdeea0-9df1-11e7-8014-06e8f9b2af92.png)\r\n\r\nShould be left aligned\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/30633498-8305f31c-9df4-11e7-9804-32a1cf9d3264.png)\r\n\r\nShould be centered\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/30633551-bc3d7b78-9df4-11e7-994d-939557667e16.png)\r\n\r\nQR windown should be bigger\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/30633603-edeeb222-9df4-11e7-9405-6af5af466543.png)\r\n\r\nIcon should be transparent\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/30633681-3e8695ec-9df5-11e7-9a69-1c0c6beb75b8.png)\r\n\r\nShould not be bold\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/30633731-6ccd120a-9df5-11e7-8e19-3118a13d53f2.png)\r\n\r\n### Expected\r\nPlease check Zeplin https://zpl.io/a3eexl2\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/30633464-67015e72-9df4-11e7-8cf4-5fdfbcfedaff.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to New wallet tab\r\n- Click Send\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: 0.9.11d117-1557.117\r\n* Operating System: iOS\r\n",
